    Class for exception that is thrown if the Proxy being accessed has already been stopped.

    SharedState
    Defines a state that is propagated to Space, Computers, and Tasks
    Space
    Defines a space that mediates between clients and connected Computers
    Task
    Defines a basic computation task on the system.
